page_title: 'How to generate reproducible output with Azure OpenAI Service'
page_description: Learn how to generate reproducible output (preview) with Azure OpenAI Service.
chunk_content: Reproducible output supportReproducible output is only currently supported with the following:### Supported models* `gpt-35-turbo` (1106)* `gpt-35-turbo` (0125)* `gpt-4` (1106-Preview)* `gpt-4` (0125-Preview)* `gpt-4` (turbo-2024-04-09)* `gpt-4o` (2024-05-13)Consult the models page for the latest information on model regional availability.### API VersionSupport for reproducible output was first added in API version `2023-12-01-preview`
